    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid choice for a driver seeking a reliable, budget-friendly commuter. Mechanically, the car is dependable; the engine starts up without issue and the transmission shifts through all gears, though you might notice some typical age-related vibrations. The exterior shows its history with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and a few minor door dings, while the interior is clean but has some visible wear on the driver's seat upholstery and a non-functional rear power window. Overall, it is a functional car that has been maintained for daily use but would benefit from some cosmetic TLC.",
