    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable daily driver for several years. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood, a few minor dings on the passenger side doors, and light scuffing on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it may benefit from a tune-up soon as the idle is slightly rough. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation without the need for perfection.",
