      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this absolute gem. Seriously, it's in such incredible shape\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You won't find a single thing out of place, inside or out. Feel free to reach out if you want to chat more about it or come take a look for yourself!",
