    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly synchronized double-VANOS system. This specimen retains its factory-spec structural integrity, with a documented subframe reinforcement and a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission that shifts with bolt-action precision. The suspension geometry is dialed to original tolerances, supported by pristine bushings and an active M-differential for optimal corner-exit bite. The chassis is free of oxidation, and the engine bay remains in a clinically clean, heat-cycle-minimal state. A purist\u2019s configuration designed for those who demand mechanical perfection.",
