      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is an absolute time capsule, presented in a flawless Guards Red over black leather interior. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the paint retains its factory-fresh depth with zero swirl marks or chips. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinctive new-car scent; the leather seats show no bolster wear, and every control feels crisp and tactile. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014full service records from the local dealership are included, showing no expense spared. It features the Premium Package, 20-inch Carrera S wheels, and a sport exhaust system that sounds incredible. If you are looking for a showroom-quality driving experience without the showroom price tag, this is the one. Includes two keys, original window sticker, and a custom car cover.",
